{"tid":2430393,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"日劇《桃色杏色櫻色》激似AV情節 兩男一女儲物櫃3P","createTime":"2021-03-03T01:55:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-03T02:16:31.000Z","uid":16659,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4c0e34deba2545b6a28670368c0a956b3d35183a","tid":2430393,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T01:55:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/BaULfJYHbK3xgtmncuL75DWbXFA=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/OTIDPXJFQ5BCNMEF4PWMCJ7T4E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FBaULfJYHbK3xgtmncuL75DWbXFA%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FOTIDPXJFQ5BCNMEF4PWMCJ7T4E.jpg&h=a04289ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大灑鹽花的日劇《桃色杏色櫻色》近日播出第二集，由前女團PASSPO ☆成員奧仲麻琴擔任女主角，飾演OL川上杏，在辦公室周旋於兩位男同事之間。岐洲匠則演男一黑田哲也，首集已有他與奧仲麻琴的肉緊床上戲，而今集更由女方採取主動，送上門之餘，更趁岐洲匠淋浴時走進浴室，兩人再由浴室錫到上床，奧仲當早上醒來時，卻發現心口出現一片紅色「咖喱雞」。<br />\n<br />\n《桃色杏色櫻色》改編自同名漫畫，為忠於原著亦不乏大膽劇情，而第二集就交代川上杏對黑田又愛又恨，今次亦有她被男方扯入公司的房間，當川上杏被黑田壓在梳化上性侵時，有人舉報該樓層有可疑人物，保安立即入房檢查，鏡頭一轉，男女主角藏身在儲物櫃之內，而櫃內竟然還有中原弘貴飾演的安藤翔，女主角被兩男夾在中間強吻，畫面似足AV情節。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/IikqAarEWZpfFE0DCdMiQxMTTNY=/802x465/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WKCDPUAL25B5RMRZYJRBHETGT4.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FIikqAarEWZpfFE0DCdMiQxMTTNY%3D%2F802x465%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWKCDPUAL25B5RMRZYJRBHETGT4.JPG&h=49ee6be7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/1lyRcJIoXTBj4fxCxjw7KlZiXMo=/802x454/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/DD6TWULQCJAMTOOGN7VHFLBT2A.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fh